name: ELECTI
description: Sometimes, being strong emotionally becomes a curse. In the purest essence of myself I feel that humans failed humanity. Sometimes things and people will hurt us. However, we also grow and progress through accepting the lessons of pain, so in a way, those who hurt are hurting. I don’t think we need a label of any kind to be the chosen one. Therefore I created this piece to remind everyone, that you are ELECTI (Chosen “in Latin), whether you were chosen by others or not, The Universe has chosen you to be here and a part of it. It is all how you perceive and look at things. You are the Chosen One.
